thread.title_full: Medisave US LLP reviewed by Danielle C

author: Danielle C
title: Danielle C
text: Ordered an engraved stethoscope and case to celebrate my husband's move to paramedic. Easy to order, competitive price and the engraving is perfect. They required signature for delivery which I did not know would happen but I was really glad because it was importnant that we received it! Will order a new one for me (nurse) soon!
